{"type": "article", "id": 10508, "title": "Roost 笔记本支架", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-08T07:06:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061358060Cseb1tJV92ZGEuW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如今，大多数人的职业病都是因为长期伏案、面对电脑而产生，比如脊椎痛、背痛、肩膀痛等等。设计师 James Olander 希望用电脑工作时能舒服点儿，于是发明了一个便携电脑支架。可以将笔记本电脑调整成最合适的角度放置，在使用电脑时帮助养成良好的坐姿。使用碳素纤维和一种超级塑料，稳固保持电脑不会受损。并配有一个耐用的尼龙袋，折叠后有约 43 厘米长并且超轻——只有 5.8 盎司。目前，这款电脑支架正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/86285180/the-roost-saving-your-neck-and-back-from-your-lapt/description\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter 网站</a>众筹，起售价 60 美元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135804gHZ5miabczI8B26s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59705882\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135804w7rMRPbCmX1gGlQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135805uidbvkVJZD3QRWPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135805PzrdnDpeKOR3uSZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}